  "title": "Fund Raising & Partnerships Executive (Healthcare, Non-Profit)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage the planning and execution of assigned <strong>fundraising events</strong> and projects from start to finish.</li>\n  <li><strong>Build and nurture partnerships</strong> by reaching out to potential sponsors, engaging stakeholders, and maintaining donor relationships.</li>\n  <li>Develop pitch decks and enhance online giving frameworks, leveraging SEO and digital marketing to optimize outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Oversee event budgets, ensuring accurate tracking of income and expenditure while adhering to fundraising requirements and governance codes.</li>\n  <li>Ensure seamless event execution through stakeholder collaboration and continuous improvement of donor engagement strategies.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Marketing or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of <strong>fundraising events and partnerships experience</strong> in a <strong>non-profit organization.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal skills and organizational skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
